title: Large Punch - Paw Print
feature: Punch Bunch Large Punches measure approximately 1 1/4 inch or 32mm.
Perfect for scrapbooking, card making and other paper craft projects
Heavy duty construction and precision-cut blades provide years of continued use
Blade can be sharpened by punching through aluminum foil or lubricated by punching through waxed paper
Punch can be stood upright or laid on its back for easy storage
description: Punch Bunch craft punches are backed by 18 years of manufacturing expertise. Heavy duty and built to last, these punches will provide years of continued use. And with hundreds of designs spanning 7 different sizes, we have the perfect shape and size for your project.
